- Oh! Such a mess.

00:58.267 --> 01:02.271
- We gotta clean you up.
- Charlie and I'll wait for you.

01:04.522 --> 01:08.110
- That was my balloon.
- Eat your ice cream before it melts.

01:08.235 --> 01:11.280
I don't want any ice cream. I want my balloon.

01:12.239 --> 01:14.283
We'll get you a balloon, OK?

01:14.408 --> 01:16.994
No. I want my balloon.

01:17.035 --> 01:19.413
Fine. We'll get you another balloon.

01:22.124 --> 01:24.585
That was a waste of good money.

01:34.553 --> 01:37.181
Ooh! There we go.

01:38.056 --> 01:40.184
Yes.

01:40.893 --> 01:42.978
OK. Ohh!

01:44.313 --> 01:47.774
There we go. That's a boy.

01:47.900 --> 01:50.611
What a good boy. OK.

01:51.612 --> 01:54.781
OK, Teddy. I'll be right back, OK?

